Belford was listed as an unincorporated community in the [[1950 U.S. census]].<ref name=CensusNJ1950CDP/> The community was not listed in subsequent censuses until the [[2000 U.S. census]] when it appeared as a [[census designated place]].<ref name=CensusNJ2000CDP/>

